加速方案提交成功: The acceleration plan is submitted successfully
系统自动生成，方案的唯一标识: Automatically generated by the system, the unique identification of the scheme
根据你的加速场景选择适用的模式: Choose the appropriate mode according to your acceleration scenario
若不开启，配置不生效: If it is not turned on, the configuration will not take effect
点击禁用当前方案，禁用后，配置将不再生效: Click to disable the current scheme, after disabling, the configuration will no longer take effect
点击开启方案，可以在构建机或流水线中使用: Click to open the solution, which can be used in the construction machine or pipeline
以汉字、英文字母、数字、连字符(-)、下划线(_)组成，不超过30个字: Consists of Chinese characters, English letters, numbers, hyphens (-), and underscores (_), no more than 30 characters
默认为“0.0.0.0”，即不限制加速任务来源。若需限制来源，请在此填写允许的来: The default is "0.0.0.0", that is, the source of acceleration tasks is not restricted. If you need to restrict the source, please fill in the allowed source IP here, separated by english semicolons.
welcome: Turbo is based on distributed compilation, cache, and container technology, aims to provide efficient, stable, and convenient acceleration services and improve development efficiency. It already supports C/C++ service compilation on Linux, as well as UE4/UE5 code compilation on Windows, macOS, and Linux, and provides acceleration services for multiple other scenarios.
